Inaccessible symbol: Term
Setting trace_terminals option
Expecting "Number" at earleme 0
Accepted "Number" at 0-1
Expecting "Multiply" at 1
Accepted "Multiply" at 1-2
Expecting "Number" at 2
Accepted "Number" at 2-3
